OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773972183
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'massively blow up'
OL,4,Cworld's largest gas field in Iran
OL,6,FDonald Trump has said the US would
OL,7,F"massively blow up the entirety" of
OL,8,Fthe world's largest gas field if Iran
OL,9,Fattacks Qatar again.
OL,11,FThe US president made his threat
OL,12,Fagainst Iran's South Pars natural gas
OL,13,Ffield on social media after Iranian
OL,14,Fmissies struck the Ras Laffan
OL,15,Fliquefied natural gas (LNG) production
OL,16,Fand export facility on Wednesday.
OL,18,FIran said the attack on Qatar was in
OL,19,Fretaliation for an Israeli attack
OL,20,Fearlier on Wednesday on the South Pars
OL,21,Fgas field.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@`O]
