OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773972183
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'massively blow up'
OL,4,Cworld's largest gas field in Iran
OL,6,FEnergy markets have faced widespread
OL,7,Fdisruption since the US and Israel's
OL,8,Fwar with Iran began on February 28,
OL,9,Fwhich has seen strikes carried out on
OL,10,Fenergy facilities and other targets in
OL,11,Foil-rich Gulf states allied with the
OL,12,FUS.
OL,14,FThe Islamic Republic has also left the
OL,15,FStrait of Hormuz, a major shipping
OL,16,Fchannel through which one-fifth of the
OL,17,Fworld's oil travels, nearly impassable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
