CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773972183
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'massively blow up'
OL,4,Cworld's largest gas field in Iran
OL,6,FGlobal oil prices rose on news of the
OL,7,FSouth Pars attack due to fears of
OL,8,FIranian retaliation on Gulf energy
OL,9,Finfrastructure.
OL,11,FTrump said in his post that the US
OL,12,F"knew nothing" about the attack, but a
OL,13,Fsource familiar with the matter said
OL,14,Fearlier on Wednesday that Washington
OL,15,Fwas informed about Israel's plans to
OL,16,Fstrike the gas field but did not take
OL,17,Fpart.
OL,26,@tD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
