FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773972183
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'massively blow up'
OL,4,Cworld's largest gas field in Iran
OL,6,FHours after the attack, authorities in
OL,7,FQatar said a ballistic missile hit the
OL,8,Fcountry's key natural gas site,
OL,9,Fsparking a fire that caused
OL,10,F"extensive" damage, and Qatar ordered
OL,11,Fsome Iranian Embassy officials out of
OL,12,Fthe country.
OL,14,FWriting on his Truth Social platform,
OL,15,FTrump said that "out of anger for what
OL,16,Fhas taken place in the Middle East",
OL,17,FIsrael had "violently lashed out" on
OL,18,Fthe South Pars gas field and stressed
OL,19,Fthat Qatar "was in no way, shape or
OL,20,Fform, involved with it".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
