OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773972183
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'massively blow up'
OL,4,Cworld's largest gas field in Iran
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, Iran did not know
OL,7,Fthis, or any of the pertinent facts
OL,8,Fpertaining to the South Pars attack,
OL,9,Fand unjustifiably and unfairly
OL,10,Fattacked a portion of Qatar's LNG Gas
OL,11,Ffacility," he added.
OL,13,F"NO MORE ATTACKS WILL BE MADE BY
OL,14,FISRAEL pertaining to this extremely
OL,15,Fimportant and valuable South Pars
OL,16,FField unless Iran unwisely decides to
OL,17,Fattack a very innocent, in this case,
OL,18,FQatar."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773972183
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'massively blow up'
OL,4,Cworld's largest gas field in Iran
OL,6,FHe wrote that if this happened again,
OL,7,F"the United States of America, with or
OL,8,Fwithout the help or consent of Israel,
OL,9,Fwill massively blow up the entirety of
OL,10,Fthe South Pars Gas Field at an amount
OL,11,Fof strength and power that Iran has
OL,12,Fnever seen or witnessed before."
OL,14,F"I do not want to authorise this level
OL,15,Fof violence and destruction because of
OL,16,Fthe long term implications that it
OL,17,Fwill have on the future of Iran, but
OL,18,Fif Qatar's LNG is again attacked, I
OL,19,Fwill not hesitate to do so," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
