PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773972183
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'massively blow up'
OL,4,Cworld's largest gas field in Iran
OL,6,FQatar warned on Thursday that
OL,7,Fadditional Iranian missile attacks
OL,8,Fdamaged more liquefied natural gas
OL,9,Fsites in the energy-rich nation,
OL,10,F"causing sizable fires and extensive
OL,11,Ffurther damage".
OL,13,FQatar Energy, the nation's state-owned
OL,14,Foil and gas company, said firefighters
OL,15,Fwere working to halt the blazes and no
OL,16,Fone had been hurt so far.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@OO]
