OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'massively blow up'
OL,4,Cworld's largest gas field in Iran
OL,6,FQatar is a key source of natural gas
OL,7,Ffor the world's energy markets. It
OL,8,Falready shut in its production earlier
OL,9,Fin the war, but extensive damage could
OL,10,Fdelay Qatar in getting its supplies to
OL,11,Fthe market after the Iran war ends.
